
[1]crepitate

   CREPITATE, v.i. [L., to crackle, to crack, to burst with a sharp
   sound.] To crackle; to snap; to burst with a small sharp abrupt sound,
   rapidly repeated; as salt in fire, or during calcination. It differs
   from detonate, which signifies, to burst with a single loud report.
     __________________________________________________________________

